<h5 class="font-weight-bold blue">The Health And Beauty Benefits</h5>
<hr class="blue">
<p style="font-size:17px !important">Cold has always been known to have phenomenal beneficial properties in the field of
medicine. Cryotherapy is a treatment which employs cold temperatures to increase
cellular survival, decrease pain and spasm, whilst promoting the constriction of blood
vessels (vasoconstriction).</p>

<p style="font-size:17px !important">In medicine, liquid nitrogen treatment is used to enhance immunity, increase circulation,
help to recover from surgeries and remove toxins from the system. It also energizes the
body due to additional release of endorphins - the body's natural painkiller. It has been
scientifically proved that Cryotherapy has been used in fields of: rheumatology, neurology,
cosmetology, orthopaedics, sexology, gynaecology, endocrinology, sports, dermatology,
and cardiology. It is a great solution for patients who deal with inter alia, rheumatoid pains,
constant headaches and orthopaedic problems. Cold therapy is also used to alleviate the
pain of injures, swelling and oedema. Some of the benefits are:</p>


